Baker and TV star Paul, who samples every contestant's fresh-baked efforts, piled on 12 pounds in the last series. He said: "I used to be involved, but now we can get 20,000 people auditioning - and I can't eat that much cake. "So I wait until I see them in the tent." The show will return next month as filming wraps up this summer. Paul, 56, was speaking while in New York on a promotional tour for his new book, Bake.